18:49.000 --> 18:51.800
<font color="#ffff00">I wanted to check the builders</font>
<font color="#ffff00">hadn't fallen behind.</font>

18:51.800 --> 18:54.800
<font color="#00ffff">At night? </font><font color="#ffff00">At night, yes. </font><font color="#ffffff">Alone?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, Jesus, Jimmy!</font>

18:54.800 --> 18:57.840
