19:18.040 --> 19:19.560
<font color="#ffffff">No, you're all right.</font>

19:19.560 --> 19:21.000
<font color="#00ffff">Do you know where Duncan is?</font>

19:21.000 --> 19:23.840
<font color="#00ffff">He left a message, it sounded odd.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I tried to give him a call back</font>

19:23.840 --> 19:26.520
<font color="#00ffff">but he's not answering.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I need to talk to you about that.</font>

19:26.520 --> 19:28.240
<font color="#ffffff">Come on inside.</font>

