24:39.880 --> 24:42.200
<font color="#ffff00">Why are you doing this to me?</font>

24:42.200 --> 24:44.600
<font color="#ffff00">Is it because of Fran</font>
<font color="#ffff00">or cos of Cass? Just so I know.</font>

24:44.600 --> 24:47.000
<font color="#ffffff">Duncan, I'm trying to help you.</font>

24:47.000 --> 24:48.840
<font color="#ffffff">Now, you listen to me.</font>

24:48.840 --> 24:51.960
<font color="#ffffff">Your DNA is on the scarf that</font>
<font color="#ffffff">killed Lizzie Kilmuir,</font>

24:51.960 --> 24:55.400
<font color="#ffffff">you were seen talking to Sally</font>
<font color="#ffffff">McColl just before she disappeared.</font>

24:55.400 --> 24:57.560
<font color="#ffffff">See that team through there?</font>

